query:
SELECT 
  po.id as pedidoId,
  po.customerOrderNumber,
  po.shippingStatus,
  i.id as nfId,
  i.invoiceNumber,
  i.status as nfStatus,
  i.pickingOrderId
FROM pickingOrders po
LEFT JOIN invoices i ON i.invoiceNumber = '1002'
WHERE po.customerOrderNumber = 'PED-0016';
